{"thag2.40:0.1":"Theragatha 2.40 ","thag2.40:0.2":"Dukanipata ","thag2.40:0.3":"Catutthavagga ","thag2.40:0.4":"Kappatakurattheragatha ","thag2.40:1.1":"“Ayamiti kappato kappatakuro, ","thag2.40:1.2":"Acchaya atibharitaya; ","thag2.40:1.3":"Amataghatikayam dhammakatamatto, ","thag2.40:1.4":"Katapadam jhanani ocetum. ","thag2.40:2.1":"Ma kho tvam kappata pacalesi, ","thag2.40:2.2":"Ma tvam upakannamhi talessam; ","thag2.40:2.3":"Na hi tvam kappata mattamannasi, ","thag2.40:2.4":"Sanghamajjhamhi pacalayamano”ti. ","thag2.40:2.5":"… Kappatakuro thero … ","thag2.40:2.6":"vaggo catuttho. ","thag2.40:3.0":"Tassuddanam ","thag2.40:3.1":"Migasiro sivako ca, ","thag2.40:3.2":"upavano ca pandito; ","thag2.40:3.3":"Isidinno ca kaccano, ","thag2.40:3.4":"nitako ca mahavasi; ","thag2.40:3.5":"Potiriyaputto nisabho, ","thag2.40:3.6":"usabho kappatakuroti. "}